Fancy has formed the cloud which hangs
over their life. Did they allow the light
of rea&s;on to break forth, the &s;pectres would
vani&s;h, and the cloud be di&s;pelled.</P>
<P>THE &s;econd ob&s;ervation on this head is,
that of tho&s;e evils which may be called real,
